      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KYVALLEY MICHAEL NZ (10) is ticking along well having finished close to the placings in both starts since a second in a higher-graded race at Melton. Draws out a little on the second line so may need luck at some point but has the talent to take this out if things go his way. ROMANTIC NINA (4) went well to finish third from the back line two starts ago then recorded a nice victory last start, scoring by 6 metres at Maryborough. This looks a sterner test than last time but she is going well enough to step up. SAM NIEN (12) disappointed as favourite last start but had kicked off his campaign with back-to-back placings. Tricky draw but he is up to winning this with his A-game. THE ITALIAN DREAM (1) won here three back and came from wider to place behind ROMANTIC NINA last start. Should get the favours from the inside draw.",
